&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Develop product and program positioning and competitively differentiated messaging based on user research, market insights, and product knowledge.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Gather customer feedback and dig into industry trends, customer use cases, and technology challenges to understand customer needs and challenges.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
